00:10:12.564 --> 00:10:16.644
longer, feature-length films, these doubts had now been erased.

00:10:17.224 --> 00:10:24.054
However, they were still incredibly expensive films to make, and film-making was a risky business.

00:10:24.994 --> 00:10:29.544
