00:10:41.144 --> 00:10:45.714
Nevertheless, Disney didn’t slow down, and the 1940s saw the

00:10:45.714 --> 00:10:50.044
creation of some of the films we now regard as timeless classics.

00:10:50.704 --> 00:10:56.684
Pinocchio and Fantasia in 1940, Dumbo in 1941, Bambi in 1942.

00:10:57.943 --> 00:11:01.574
