00:11:25.150 --> 00:11:32.520
it wasn’t until the 1950s that he started to produce hit films again, such as Cinderella, in 1950.

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:39.170
By this time, Walt Disney was dreaming bigger and bigger, and of diversifying.

00:11:40.290 --> 00:11:46.100
In 1953, after the release of Peter Pan, he created a film production

00:11:46.100 --> 00:11:51.060
company called Buena Vista, which started off by making nature documentaries.

00:11:51.610 --> 00:11:56.070
