00:13:30.062 --> 00:13:36.794
So, by the early 1960s, Disney hadn’t only cemented its reputation as the world’s favourite

00:13:36.844 --> 00:13:43.688
producer of cartoons, but had branched out into nature films, theme parks, and merchandise.

00:13:44.868 --> 00:13:49.748
